Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Taihei... can I come by your place for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why don't you come as well, Alex? Sometimes, it's-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Tanukichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hi, Bomba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, who's THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Alex. He works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.54,0:02:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I am STARVING!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for dragging you along...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty clueless, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This was your BOSS asking you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel kind of like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,like I've seen him somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hotpot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's pretty much in season,\Nso it should taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, autumn is the time for eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Autumn"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight's a parade of autumn specials!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Autumn variety shows! Autumn anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Anime Song Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Autumn variety shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Autumn anime shows!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing it! It's the anime song festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,YAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, yay, yay, yay-yay-yay, yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even live here,\Nbut he's really getting worked up! Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this feeling, of someone being all excited\Nbut not caring about ME. But from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese animation is cute and cool!\NMy older brother loves it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be Sylphyn's brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! Now that I look closely, he TOTALLY\Nseems like he could be her brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But, wait, that's too much of a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't watch anime at all. Isn't that just for kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NAnime is a part of Japanese culture!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This HAS to be Sylphyn's brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... therefore I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I think? This was a quality show,\Nand I'm sad to see it end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! I've been a fan of the show too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the merch and the Blu-rays and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,M-me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Only, yappari Japan ga suki desu wa\NOnly, sure enough, I love Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!\NIchiban ga ichiban oniai no\NOnly the best for the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichiban ga ichiban oniai no\NOnly the best for the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pow, pow!\NKisoiai futari, yuujou wa\NOur friendship, the two of us competing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisoiai futari, yuujou wa\NOur friendship, the two of us competing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!\NUtsukushii mono desu wa\NIs a beautiful thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Utsukushii mono desu wa\NIs a beautiful thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurinchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they've suddenly become friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pow, pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...the power of anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me, I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru, you certainly know a lot about anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no slacker yourself, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're already this buddy-buddy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right if I come by with some\Nof my favorite Blu-Rays sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that, Umaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like Alex had a good time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even at the office, Alex just seems sort of OFF, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they did bring him on as a special hire...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, why WAS he a special hire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? This is Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have made contact... with Umaru Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? Isn't your reaction sort of LACKING?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting like spies should be more fun, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Umaru. If you're going to use my ear pick,\Nyou could at least give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her to give it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll just... buy one on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone, gone, still gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My ear's all itchy, but the ear pick is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And it should be right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's making me feel all creepy-crawly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She suffers! Yes, she suffers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we won't be seeing\Nthat stick today, huh, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come for her to know how much\Nwe despise that stick's daily intrusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and give her the greatest itch you can. Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\NGo and give her the greatest itch you can. Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go! Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!\NWoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,HELP ME, BIG BROTHER!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, you're out early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some shopping to do.\NI stepped on my ear pick and broke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ear pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru used it and left it lying out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanukichi must have it rough right now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What? She just used it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's right after you use it that the itching is worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My ears itch! Help me, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My ears aren't right! They just aren't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But my finger can't go all the way in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you Tanukichi would be suffering...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your own fault for not putting things away, Umaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, just hand it over, Bomba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We bought one of each that they had at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bomba said he wanted to try out some different kinds...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew there were so many different ear picks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Check this out. This thing looks AWESOME.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Screwdriver!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's effective not just in one direction,\Nbut in ALL directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Three tiers of wires!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Each twist has three times the results,\Nwhich means less work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A FLASHLIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This will let you see the deepest parts of your ear,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:09:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,for maximum focus yet little strain on your aural orifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are other options as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We did good, huh? She looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to pay me back for all this stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one's easiest to use?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't tried them all yet, so I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This sure takes me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The only time someone cleans your ears\Nfor you is when you're a kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And your mom does it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Taihei, do me next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:09:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Heard what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They say Umaru's brother\Nis some totally handsome actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And supposedly, her dad is German!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She really is cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's German... and Taihei is a handsome actor?\NShe really is cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's German... and Taihei is a handsome actor?\NI know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's German... and Taihei is a handsome actor?\NSo cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where these rumors are coming from,\Nbut they keep spreading and changing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,UMR!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shwpa-pa-pa-pa-pa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shbwaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've kept you waiting indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to ask your advice on something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I didn't think Sylphyn would be the type\Nto sit down and talk like this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,sure enough, you can't trust every rumor you hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sorry, I didn't catch what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:11:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,UMR, I would like to invite you over\Nto my house today. Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have hopscotch stepping stones!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three! One, two, three! One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sliding indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is so big...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like it has some history to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anime is a part of Japanese culture!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,OH, yeah... Sylphyn and Alex\Nare brother and sister, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:12:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a weekday, so I guess he's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right down this stairway, UMR!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she going to try something\Ndown there in the basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Look at all these books!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, we should study for our tests!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for midterm exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume you have them at your school as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We do, but... wait, we're at the SAME school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I WILL get a better score than Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think you can beat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Umaru" you're talking about\Nis right here in front of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I read poetry in our house's library.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a one-room apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your score?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what it will take to beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I always study in our private library.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I am Sylphynford Tachibana.\NMy father is German and my mother is Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They say Umaru's house has its own library.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... I wonder if she studies poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, UMR?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just... you can't trust rumors, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumors? I would like to hear more of this indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what sort of rumors are these, UMR?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,UMARU!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! What, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even time for spring cleaning yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen closely, Umaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't just about cleaning:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about your attitude,\Nand how you don't care how dirty things get.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a detox, for the soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what I mean is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I clean every week, but when\Nthe weekend comes, it's dirty again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're being lazy! You think it's okay\Nto leave things messy and I'll clean it up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I didn't make a mess, you'd have nothing\Nto do on the weekends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I look all shriveled up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we're doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleaning Technique No. 1: Decide What Goes Where!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This place gets messy because\Nthings are just left scattered all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:15:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we have to decide\Nwhere each and every item goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to use the bookshelves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Big Brother learned his technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,From THIS, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We've pretty much figured out where things go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's a whole bunch still left over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleaning Technique No. 2:\NStore Whatever Remains Left from Step 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't come up with a place for something,\Nit means you don't use it much and you should store it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's box up volumes\Nof the same size and genre together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But Big Brother, what "genre" is it\Nif you've got a DVD inside of a game case?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have things all mixed up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pain to keep pulling discs out and\Nputting them back in, so I just put them wherever...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Put them back in their proper cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's everything nice and stored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:16:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But if there's no more room to put stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Presenting Cleaning Technique No. 3:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You toss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,HUH?! No way! That would be a waste!\NI mean, look how cute this doll thing is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You call that "cute"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen closely, Umaru:\NAll things are destined to meet their end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Out with the old and in with the new!\NThis is the natural order of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Out with the old and in with the new!\NThis is the natural order of things!\NHup, hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The sticky note on this page here\Nsays the same thing that you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,M-maybe I could keep that\Nstuffed doll of yours on my desk...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks pretty clean, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying leap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to see\Nif you can keep things nice and neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bored of this game... oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll play one of those retro games\Nthat turned up yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun to play these once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have things all mixed up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Which case did this belong to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru... You can leave things a LITTLE messy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's all shriveled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going somewhere on Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to the movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a big crowd indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've seen a movie at the theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Should we watch it first, or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it is almost lunch time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphyn has already bought popcorn\Nand is standing in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shbwaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sylphyn! You're already in line?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've bought popcorn for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We were talking about getting something to eat first...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shwaaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you were?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphyn, I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um, maybe we COULD see the movie first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There sure are a lot of movies out, huh?\NWhich one should we see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That hasn't come out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so sweet and delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop eating it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They all look good... it's hard to choose one, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Master Detective Nacon" seems pretty popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! 4.5 stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to watch Nacon when I was in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to see Precuare!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! You already bought the promotional booklet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That caters to an even younger audience...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay everyone, let's all raise our voices!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Precuare!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'd be a little embarrassed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But I spent last night watching\Nthe old shows and practicing for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as I can be with the Master...\NI'm totally fine with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go with what everyone wants to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I will see Precuare with UMR later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a DJ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is comfy indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What happened to the popcorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We were lucky to find such good seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought the four of us would be\Nhanging out and watching a movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm glad we were all able to become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A-are you okay, Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine! I'm just a little scared of the dark.\NBut I'll be all right. Please, enjoy the movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,An incident this week! An incident next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He goes to the movies and a bomb goes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, too, his deductive powers will leap into action!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He is Master Detective Nacon!\NAnd catastrophe awaits him at the restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... so this is the restaurant run\Nby that friend of Zonoko's uncle, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear a scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well. This is an interesting start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However! I'll be looking at all the clues\Nthat they drop and I will figure out the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what the others think...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sylphyn's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:21:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But I spent last night watching\Nthe old shows and practicing for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me she stayed up till morning\Nwatching all those seasons of Precuare!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have solved the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit added poison to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the "Mediterranean Breeze Course Menu"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what should I do? My stomach is about to growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let that happen here - it's too embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna blow this restaurant up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I fell asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness. It looks like everyone\Nwas focused on the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nacon did a better job than me\Nat figuring out the culprit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.79,0:23:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My ears are itching again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We earwax shall destroy you!\NYour ears will itch and itch again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.25,0:23:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, not even I have seen an anime\Nthat has earwax in the next episode preview!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.21,0:23:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you watching, you will be reduced\Nto a piteous state and made to itch as well!
